Our nearest US higher headquarters and primary source of resource support came from the Central European Region (primarily Germany and Italy). Worked very closely with the United Nations Headquarters based out of Skopje, as well as with our counterparts from the Nordic Battalion (comprised of Soldiers from Finland, Sweden, and Norway).
name: Bill McClary
